DEPARTMENT OF BUSINESS ADMINISTRATION
Ph.D. in Management and Organization

Book Summary
Sun Tzu – The Art of War


Submitted by
Özgür Önday




Submitted to
Prof. Dr. İlhan Atilla Dicle


2013-2014 FALL

